+ * STATUS_TIMEOUT (not STATUS_ALERTED). The original drain-on-ALERTED branch
+ * triggered TH-U's drag-drop crash at TH-U+0x1802DF0C3 by dispatching
+ * cross-thread sends re-entrantly inside the receiver's mid-flight
